flowchart TB
    A[Agent generates command] --> D{Denylist}
    D -->|match| R[Refused]
    D -->|no match| S[LocalSandbox]
    S --> C[tokio::process::Command]
    C -->|env_clear, current_dir| P[Subprocess]
    P --> T[Wall-clock timeout]
    P --> O[Output cap]
    T -->|deadline| K[kill_on_drop]
    O -->|cap hit| TR[truncated]
    P --> X[exit code]
    X --> ER[ExecResult]
    K --> ER
    TR --> ER

    style D fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828,color:#000
    style S fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    style ER fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
